data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Trust the Compass Rose to navigate you to the place you are meant to be! Amazingly warm and welcoming Pulte built residence on an expansive corner lot is ready for new homeowners. Laminate plank floors guide you from the entry to the rear of the home seamlessly. Walk into the oversized front room perfect for gathering and entertaining family and friends. Continue deeper in the house to find an open concept kitchen looking over the dining area flowing into the cozy living area perfect for relaxing.  Pop out the sliding glass doors into the lanai for a little outdoor time before passing through the open outdoor patio area enclosed in a newly fenced backyard.  The lanai already has a doggie door perfect for your pooch! The primary suite entrance is located in the rear of the home. The bright ensuite bathroom has dual sinks, separate shower, soaking tub and walk-in closet. The secondary bedrooms can be accessed down the hallway with access to the main bathroom. A spacious laundry room with built-in cabinets is just off the 2-car garage with epoxy floors. The community has stellar amenities for fairly low fees which include clubhouse, pool, a park, playground, and tennis courts. Easy access to I-75 for commuting and shopping. Don't miss out on this warm and inviting home. SELLER OFFERING $5000 TOWARDS BUYER'S CLOSING COSTS
